item.title: MMELO @ CMOA
item.description:
MMELO @ CMOA

We are absolutely thrilled to announce a small range of MMELO goodies are now available at the Columbus Museum of Art ..!This Banana Caramel tea cake in a tropical blue sea is a custom CMOA Van Gogh inspired color finish, and only available in the Museum Store. Treat your eyes with a visit to the fantastic newly opened Margaret M Walter Wing of the Museum, and your taste buds with a visit to their store.
